Read the file called COPYRIGHT.

On AIX, type "./config.sh && gmake".
On other platforms, type "./config.sh && make" (as long as this is GNU make).

Or if you want to alter the compiler, you can run
% make CC=foobar

Install detail see the file called INSTALL.

Usage:
See tpty(1), tptyreplay(1), tpty-crypt(1) manual and samples under sample directory.

Please, send all your reports, patches and suggestions to <gong_cun@bocmacau.com>,
Developers are welcome.

Cun Gong
gong_cun@bocmacau.com

